OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start, perhaps frosty,
OL,6,Fbut largely dry with sunny spells
OL,7,Fduring the morning, turning cloudier
OL,8,Fduring the afternoon. Chance of some
OL,9,Flight rain in the north. Cloud
OL,10,Fbreaking with some further sunny
OL,11,Fspells late in the afternoon. Light
OL,12,Fwinds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSome early evening sunny
OL,15,Fspells before cloud increasing from
OL,16,Fthe north. Band of rain, perhaps heavy
OL,17,Fat times, moving south overnight.
OL,18,FBecoming breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
