OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FLargely dry and bright with
OL,6,Fsunny intervals and a few coastal
OL,7,Fshowers. Breezy, though strong winds
OL,8,Fnear coasts.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,11,Fand cloudy, with rain Tuesday morning,
OL,12,Ffollowed by showers. Blustery showers,
OL,13,Fwith possible thunder, and sunny
OL,14,Fintervals Wednesday and Thursday. Cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
